  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a panini press to 375 degrees Fahrenheit",
    "Spread mayonnaise on each slice of double-rise bread",
    "Layer shredded chicken breast, sliced morbier cheese, pickled jalapeno, and caramelized onions on two slices of bread",
    "Sprinkle turmeric, ginger, salt, and black pepper on top of the filling",
    "Place the other two slices of bread on top of the filling to create a sandwich",
    "Place the sandwiches in the panini press and cook for 5 minutes",
    "Remove the sandwiches from the press and sprinkle chopped cilantro on top",
    "Cut the sandwiches in half and serve immediately",
    "Serve with a side of tomato soup to help cool down the palate"
  ],
